Package: cleverbox 
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, subversion (>=1.4.2), trac (>=0.10), libapache2-mod-python (>=3.2.10), libapache2-svn (>=1.4.2), python-setuptools (>=0.6c3-3)
Conflicts:  trac-0.10.3 
Suggests: libapache2-mod-macro 
Description: Trac and Subversion instances deployment shell 
 The cleverbox provides an interactive command line shell dedicated to the 
 deployment and maintenance of trac and subversion instances.
 It can handle multiple configuration profiles, enabling the deployment 
 of differently flavored type of projects :  
 trac configuration and permissions, apache configuration templates, etc.
 Project's main objective is to make your life as simple as possible. 
 Thus, it comes with easy installation, easy upgrades and a comprehensive
 documentation.